    <p><span>A girl from Liberl Kingdom training to become a Bracer.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Nihon Falcom [732 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nihon-falcom">Falcom</a> has released the first character trailer for <em><a title="Games > Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter">Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</a></em>, introducing protagonist Estelle Bright. <span id="more-973327"></span></p><p>Here is her official description:</p><blockquote><p>A bright and determined Bracer trainee of the Guild.</p><p>A girl from Liberl Kingdom training to become a Bracer in order to protect the safety of civilians and peace of cities.</p><p>A bright, outgoing, and optimistic girl who never gives up, no matter the situation. Her sincere nature leads her to trust others easily, and her actions are often impulsive.</p><p>Trained by her father, a veteran Bracer, she possesses considerable combat skills. For the past 5 years, she has been striving to become a Senior Bracer alongside her adopted younger brother, Joshua.</p></blockquote><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><em>Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,720 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,211 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,495 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3375780/Trails_in_the_Sky_1st_Chapter/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on September 19 worldwide. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/03/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-main-characters-voice-cast">here</a> and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-more-characters-battle-system">here</a>.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Character Trailer: Estelle Bright</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="【エステル】キャラクタームービー #空の軌跡the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UeUmFVUauyM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Korean</strong></p><p><iframe title="【에스텔】 캐릭터 무비 #하늘의궤적 #the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sD45eoxJ8GQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe title="【艾絲蒂爾】 角色影片 #空之軌跡the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wjhTSkLdxqs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscree